<div class="main article-index bg-image3">

  <div class="top-bar">
    <h1>Article</h1>
    <p>「まずは小さな一歩から」なんて、当たり前のようで難しい。<br>
          そんなあなたの勇気になるように。<br>
          一歩踏み出す決意をしたメンバーの声を集めました。
</p>
  </div> <!-- /.top-bar -->

  <div class="contents-bar">
    <div class="article-box">

      <% @articles.each do |article| %>
        <a href="/articles/<%= article.id %>" class="link-to-article">

          <div class="article-contents">
            <div class="article-sumbnail"><%= image_tag article.image_name, :width =>'290', :height =>'200' %></div>

              <p class="article-title"><%= article.title %></p>

              <div class="article-info">
                    <div class="writer-img">
                      <%= image_tag article.writer.image_name, :size => '50x50' %>
                    </div>
                    <p class="writer-name"><%= article.writer.name %></p>
              </div><!-- /.article-info -->

          </div><!-- /.article-contents -->
        </a>
      <% end %>

      </div><!-- /.article-box -->
    </div><!-- /.contents-bar -->
  </div><!-- /.main article-index -->




</div>
